{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"你當讚頌你至尊主的大名超絕萬物，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他創造萬物，並使各物勻稱。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他預定萬物，而加以引導。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"他生出牧草，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"然後使它變成黑色的枯草。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"我將使你誦讀，故你不會忘記，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"除非真主所欲你忘記的。他的確知道顯著的和隱微的言行。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"我將使你遵循平易的道路，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"故你當教誨眾人，如果教誨有裨於他們的話。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"畏主的人，將覺悟；"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"薄命的人，將退避，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"他將入於大火，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"然後，在火裡不死也不活。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"有教養的人確已成功，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"他記念他的主的尊名，而謹守拜功。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"不然，你們卻選擇今世的生活；"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"其實，後世是更好的，是更久長的。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"這確是載在古經典中的，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"載在易卜拉欣和穆薩的經典中的。"}]}